AICTE Pragati Scholarship Purpose: Support female students pursuing technical education. Eligibility: Female students in 1st year (or lateral entry 2nd year) of technical degree/diploma at AICTE institutions; family income < ₹8 lakh; max 2 girls per family. Benefits: ₹50,000 per annum (lump sum) for academic expenses. Application: Online via National Scholarship Portal (https://scholarships.go